credit.credit-words: and he that believeth not the Son shall not see life..." (John 3:36).
"He that believeth on the Son hath everlasting life:
should be the great and solemn question with us now."
"The concerns of eternity are of sufficient importance to take precedence over every other enterprise. ‘What must I do to be saved?'
"The perils of the last days are upon us, and at this time we are each determining what our destiny for eternity shall be. Individually we are to form characters
that will stand the test of the judgment."
